  "claim": {
    "statement": "Prefer undo over up-front confirmation for reversible actions. Where an action can be safely reversed, perform it immediately and offer a time-boxed undo (e.g. a toast), which is lower friction and lets users recover from mistakes without dialog fatigue.",
